description: Creates a domain name access association resource between an access association source and a private custom domain name.

parameters.name: domainNameArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the domain name.

parameters.name: accessAssociationSourceType
parameters.description: The type of the domain name access association source.

parameters.name: accessAssociationSource
parameters.description: The identifier of the domain name access association source. For a VPCE, the value is the VPC endpoint ID.

parameters.name: tags
parameters.description: The key-value map of strings. The valid character set is [a-zA-Z+-=._:/]. The tag key can be up to 128 characters and must not start with aws:. The tag value can be up to 256 characters. (string) --- (string) ---

nested_items.name: domainNameAccessAssociationArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the domain name access association resource.

nested_items.name: domainNameArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the domain name.

nested_items.name: accessAssociationSourceType
nested_items.description: The type of the domain name access association source.

nested_items.name: accessAssociationSource
nested_items.description: The ARN of the domain name access association source. For a VPCE, the ARN must be a VPC endpoint.
